#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>\n"
"                <strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">Bike Shop</span></"
"strong>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            <br/>"
msgstr ""
"<strong>\n"
"                <strong><span class=\"display-4-fs\">ຮ້ານລົດຖີບ (Bike Shop)</"
"span></strong>\n"
"            </strong>\n"
"            <br/>"

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Add vendor lead times</strong> on each product to anticipate "
"delivery delays and organize procurement planning accordingly (e.g., 5-day "
"lead time for imported suspension forks)."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເພີ່ມໄລຍະເວລາລໍຖ້າຂອງຜູ້ສະໜອງ (Vendor Lead Times)</strong> "
"ໃນແຕ່ລະສິນຄ້າເພື່ອຄາດຄະເນຄວາມລ່າຊ້າຂອງການຈັດສົ່ງ ແລະ ຈັດລະບຽບການວາງແຜນການຈັດຊື້ໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມ "
"(ຕົວຢ່າງ: ໄລຍະເວລາລໍຖ້າ 5 ວັນສຳລັບໂຊ້ກລົດຖີບທີ່ນຳເຂົ້າ)."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Automated Reordering</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ການສັ່ງຊື້ຄືນແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong>"

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Based on the brand’s response</strong>, check or uncheck the "
"<strong>\"Warranty\" box</strong> on the Workshop task to reflect whether "
"the repair is covered."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ອີງຕາມການຕອບກັບຂອງແບຣນ</strong>, ໃຫ້ໝາຍ ຫຼື ຍົກເລີກການໝາຍໃນ <strong>ຫ້ອງ "
"\"ການຮັບປະກັນ (Warranty)\"</strong> ໃນໜ້າວຽກຂອງ Workshop "
"ເພື່ອສະແດງໃຫ້ເຫັນວ່າການສ້ອມແປງນັ້ນໄດ້ຮັບການຄຸ້ມຄອງຫຼືບໍ່."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.repairs
msgid "<strong>Common Repairs We Offer</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ການສ້ອມແປງທົ່ວໄປທີ່ພວກເຮົາໃຫ້ບໍລິການ</strong>"

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Configure Optional Products: </strong>Suggest relevant accessories "
"such as helmets, locks, or lights by configuring them as <strong>optional "
"products</strong>, which appear during checkout to encourage upselling."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ຕັ້ງຄ່າສິນຄ້າທາງເລືອກ: </strong>ແນະນຳອຸປະກອນເສີມທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ ເຊັ່ນ: ໝວກກັນກະທົບ, "
"ກະແຈລັອກ, ຫຼື ໄຟ ໂດຍການຕັ້ງຄ່າໃຫ້ເປັນ <strong>ສິນຄ້າທາງເລືອກ (Optional Products)</"
"strong>, ເຊິ່ງຈະປາກົດຂຶ້ນໃນເວລາຊຳລະເງິນເພື່ອສົ່ງເສີມການຂາຍເພີ່ມ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create a Sales Order</strong> for a maintenance or specific repair "
"directly from the Sales app."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສ້າງໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ (Sales Order)</strong> ສຳລັບການບຳລຸງຮັກສາ ຫຼື "
"ການສ້ອມແປງສະເພາະໂດຍກົງຈາກແອັບການຂາຍ (Sales)."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Create a ticket</strong> to verify the warranty. You can also "
"<strong>automate ticket creation</strong> by sharing the email alias (e.g. "
"warranties@bike-shop.odoo.com); when clients send an email, a ticket is "
"created\n"
"                        automatically."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສ້າງທິກເກັດ (Ticket)</strong> ເພື່ອກວດສອບການຮັບປະກັນ. ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດ "
"<strong>ຕັ້ງຄ່າການສ້າງທິກເກັດແບບອັດຕະໂນມັດ</strong> ໂດຍການແບ່ງປັນນາມແຝງອີເມວ (ເຊັ່ນ "
"warranties@bike-shop.odoo.com); ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າສົ່ງອີເມວມາ, ທິກເກັດຈະຖືກສ້າງຂຶ້ນ\n"
"                        ໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Customize customer notifications</strong>: Personalize the "
"<strong>\"Order Ready\"</strong> email by enabling <strong>Debug Mode</"
"strong>, navigating to <em>Email Templates</em>, and editing\n"
"                    <strong>\"Sales Order: Order Ready\"</strong>. You can "
"also configure automated messages via <strong>SMS</strong> and "
"<strong>WhatsApp</strong> using Odoo’s marketing automation and messaging "
"integrations"
msgstr ""
"<strong>ປັບແຕ່ງການແຈ້ງເຕືອນລູກຄ້າ</strong>: ປັບແຕ່ງອີເມວ <strong>\"Order Ready\"</"
"strong> ໃຫ້ເປັນແບບຂອງທ່ານເອງ ໂດຍການເປີດໃຊ້ <strong>Debug Mode</strong>, ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ "
"<em>Email Templates</em>, ແລະ ແກ້ໄຂ\n"
"                    <strong>\"Sales Order: Order Ready\"</strong>. "
"ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດຕັ້ງຄ່າຂໍ້ຄວາມອັດຕະໂນມັດຜ່ານ <strong>SMS</strong> ແລະ <strong>WhatsApp</"
"strong> ໂດຍໃຊ້ການຕະຫຼາດອັດຕະໂນມັດ ແລະ ການເຊື່ອມຕໍ່ລະບົບຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງ Odoo"

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Customize your project stages</strong> in the “Workshop” project: "
"add columns like “Waiting for Parts” to better track blocked repairs waiting "
"for a parts delivery, or “Ready for Pick-Up\" when the repair is done."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ປັບແຕ່ງຂັ້ນຕອນຂອງໂຄງການ (Project Stages)</strong> ໃນໂຄງການ “Workshop”: "
"ເພີ່ມຖັນ (columns) ເຊັ່ນ “Waiting for Parts” "
"ເພື່ອຕິດຕາມການສ້ອມແປງທີ່ຕິດຂັດຍ້ອນລໍຖ້າການຈັດສົ່ງອາໄຫຼ່, ຫຼື “Ready for Pick-Up\" "
"ເມື່ອການສ້ອມແປງສຳເລັດແລ້ວ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Do the repair</strong>, add any parts used, and mark the task as "
"Done when done."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ດຳເນີນການສ້ອມແປງ</strong>, ເພີ່ມຊິ້ນສ່ວນ/ອາໄຫຼ່ທີ່ນຳໃຊ້, ແລະ ໝາຍໜ້າວຽກວ່າ ສຳເລັດ "
"(Done) ເມື່ອເຮັດແລ້ວ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Filter repair tasks by Serial Number</strong> to view a bike’s "
"repair history; helpful for recurring maintenance actions like annual oil "
"checks on specific components."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ກັ່ນຕອງໜ້າວຽກການສ້ອມແປງຕາມເລກຊຸດ (Serial Number)</strong> "
"ເພື່ອເບິ່ງປະຫວັດການສ້ອມແປງຂອງລົດຖີບ; ເປັນປະໂຫຍດສຳລັບການບຳລຸງຮັກສາທີ່ເຮັດເປັນປະຈຳ ເຊັ່ນ: "
"ການກວດເຊັກນ້ຳມັນປະຈຳປີຂອງບາງຊິ້ນສ່ວນສະເພາະ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Finish the payment</strong> when the customer picks up the bike; "
"directly from the PoS using the linked order."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ສຳເລັດການຊຳລະເງິນ</strong> ເມື່ອລູກຄ້າາມາຮັບລົດຖີບ; ໂດຍກົງຈາກ PoS "
"ໂດຍໃຊ້ການສັ່ງຊື້ທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງໄວ້."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Handle warranty cases through the Helpdesk app:</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ຈັດການກໍລະນີການຮັບປະກັນຜ່ານແອັບ Helpdesk:</strong>"

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "<strong>Inventory &amp; Stock Replenishment</strong>"
msgstr "<strong>ສາງສິນຄ້າ ແລະ ການເຕີມສິນຄ້າໃນສາງ</strong>"

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"<strong>Link the ticket</strong> to the related <strong>Sales Order Line</"
"strong> and the matching <strong>Workshop task</strong> (e.g. repair on the "
"client’s Cube bike). Move the ticket to the\n"
"                        <strong>“Sent to Brand”</strong> column and use an "
"<strong>Email Template</strong> to contact the brand for warranty "
"confirmation."
msgstr ""
"<strong>ເຊື່ອມໂຍງທິກເກັດ</strong> ກັບ <strong>ລາຍການໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ (Sales Order Line)</"
