#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage bike parts and inventory efficiently using the <strong>Purchase</"
"strong> and <strong>Inventory</strong> apps to avoid shortages and "
"streamline restocking."
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການອາໄຫຼ່ລົດຖີບ ແລະ ສາງສິນຄ້າຢ່າງມີປະສິດທິພາບ ໂດຍໃຊ້ແອັບ <strong>ການຈັດຊື້ (Purchase)</"
"strong> ແລະ <strong>ສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)</strong> ເພື່ອຫຼີກເວັ້ນສິນຄ້າຂາດສາງ ແລະ "
"ເຮັດໃຫ້ການເຕີມສິນຄ້າມີຄວາມຄ່ອງຕົວ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Manage in-store transactions for bikes, accessories, or specific parts with "
"the<strong> Point of Sale (PoS) </strong>app.<strong/><br/>"
msgstr ""
"ຈັດການການເຮັດທຸລະກຳພາຍໃນຮ້ານສຳລັບລົດຖີບ, ອຸປະກອນເສີມ, ຫຼື ອາໄຫຼ່ສະເພາະ ດ້ວຍແອັບ "
"<strong>ຈຸດຂາຍ (PoS)</strong>.<strong/><br/>"

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Mark the task as <strong>Done</strong> when completed. Once all tasks linked "
"to the Sales Order are in this stage, a <strong>notification email</strong> "
"will automatically be sent to the customer confirming that their bike\n"
"                    is ready."
msgstr ""
"ໝາຍໜ້າວຽກວ່າ <strong>ສຳເລັດ (Done)</strong> ເມື່ອເຮັດແລ້ວ. "
"ເມື່ອທຸກໜ້າວຽກທີ່ເຊື່ອມໂຍງກັບໃບສັ່ງຂາຍຢູ່ໃນຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້, <strong>ອີເມວແຈ້ງເຕືອນ</strong> "
"ຈະຖືກສົ່ງໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າໂດຍອັດຕະໂນມັດ ເພື່ອຢືນຢັນວ່າລົດຖີບຂອງພວກເຂົາ\n"
"                    ກຽມພ້ອມແລ້ວ."

