#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Odoo is entirely integrated into an App. Download it to turn your phone to "
"manage your entire business in it."
msgstr ""
"Odoo ໄດ້ຖືກເຊື່ອມໂຍງເຂົ້າໃນແອັບດຽວຢ່າງສົມບູນ. "
"ດາວໂຫຼດມັນເພື່ອປ່ຽນໂທລະສັບຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເປັນເຄື່ອງມືຈັດການທຸລະກິດທັງໝົດຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Of course, this is just an overview of the features included in this "
"package. Feel free to add new apps, delete/modify demo data, and test "
"everything around!"
msgstr ""
"ແນ່ນອນວ່າ, ນີ້ເປັນພຽງພາບລວມຂອງຟີເຈີທີ່ມີຢູ່ໃນແພັກເກັດນີ້. ທ່ານສາມາດເພີ່ມແອັບໃໝ່, ລຶບ/ແກ້ໄຂຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງ, "
"ແລະ ທົດລອງໃຊ້ທຸກຢ່າງໄດ້ຕາມສະບາຍ!"

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once all tasks related to the Sales Order are \"Marked as Done\"<strong> </"
"strong>column, the order becomes <strong>Collectible</strong>. An<strong> </"
"strong>automation sends an email to the customer, notifying them that the\n"
"                bike is ready for pickup."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອທຸກໜ້າວຽກທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງກັບໃບສັ່ງຂາຍຖືກ \"ໝາຍວ່າສຳເລັດ (Marked as Done)\"<strong></"
"strong> ແລ້ວ, ການສັ່ງຊື້ຈະກາຍເປັນ <strong>ກຽມພ້ອມໃຫ້ມາຮັບ (Collectible). </"
"strong><strong></strong>ລະບົບອັດຕະໂນມັດຈະສົ່ງອີເມວຫາລູກຄ້າ ເພື່ອແຈ້ງໃຫ້ພວກເຂົາຮູ້ວ່າ\n"
"                ລົດຖີບກຽມພ້ອມສຳລັບການມາຮັບແລ້ວ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Once the purchase is confirmed, send the <strong>Request for Quotation "
"(RFQ)</strong> via email or confirm it manually."
msgstr ""
"ເມື່ອການຈັດຊື້ໄດ້ຮັບການຢືນຢັນແລ້ວ, ໃຫ້ສົ່ງ <strong>ໃບຮ້ອງຂໍລາຄາ (RFQ)</strong> ຜ່ານອີເມວ ຫຼື "
"ຢືນຢັນດ້ວຍຕົນເອງ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the Point of Sale App and start a session by clicking on your register."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດແອັບຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of Sale) ແລະ ເລີ່ມການເຮັດວຽກໂດຍການຄລິກທີ່ເຄື່ອງບັນທຶກເງິນຂອງທ່ານ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid "Open the Sales app from the main dashboard."
msgstr "ເປີດແອັບ Sales ຈາກໜ້າຈໍຫຼັກ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Open the<strong> Field Service app</strong> and check your assigned tasks or "
"priorities."
msgstr ""
"ເປີດ<strong> ແອັບ Field Service</strong> ແລະ ກວດເຊັກໜ້າວຽກທີ່ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບມອບໝາຍ ຫຼື "
"ບຸລິມະສິດ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"Organize products by category (e.g., VTT, Cargo, Electric) to help users "
