"ແອັບ\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">ການຈັດຊື້ App "
"</font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;"
"\">m</span></font>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    <font class=\"text-o-color-5\">anages</font> "
"ຈັດການການສັ່ງຊື້ຈາກຜູ້ສະໜອງ ແລະ ການເຕີມລົດຖີບ ລວມທັງອາໄຫຼ່ເຂົ້າສາງ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">eCommerce "
"App </font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;"
"\">s</span></font>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    ell bikes and accessories online with a customizable web "
"store."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບ\n"
"                    <strong>\n"
"                        <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">eCommerce "
"App </font><font class=\"text-o-color-5\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;"
"\">s</span></font>\n"
"                    </strong>\n"
"                    ຂາຍລົດຖີບ ແລະ ອຸປະກອນເສີມອອນລາຍ ດ້ວຍເວັບໄຊຮ້ານຄ້າທີ່ປັບແຕ່ງໄດ້."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\"><strong>Helpdesk App</strong></"
"font> manages warranty claims, after-sales support, and repair requests."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບ <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\"><strong>Helpdesk</strong></"
"font> ຈັດການການຮ້ອງຂໍການຮັບປະກັນ, ການຊ່ວຍເຫຼືອຫຼັງການຂາຍ, ແລະ ຄຳຮ້ອງຂໍການສ້ອມແປງ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The<strong> </strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);"
"\"><strong>Website App</strong></font> manages your online presence and "
"allow customers to book appointments or test rides."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບ <strong> </strong><font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);"
"\"><strong>ເວັບໄຊ</strong></font>ຈັດການຕົວຕົນອອນລາຍຂອງທ່ານ ແລະ "
"ອະນຸຍາດໃຫ້ລູກຄ້າຈອງນັດໝາຍ ຫຼື ລອງຂີ່ລົດຖີບ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The<strong> <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Inventory App</font></"
"strong> tracks bike and parts stock, including serial numbers and stock "
"movement."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບ <strong> <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">ສາງສິນຄ້າ (Inventory)</"
"font></strong> ຕິດຕາມສາງລົດຖີບ ແລະ ອາໄຫຼ່, ລວມທັງເລກຊຸດ ແລະ ການເຄື່ອນໄຫວຂອງສິນຄ້າ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The<strong> <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Point of Sale (PoS)</"
"font></strong> manages bike and accessory sales directly in the store."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບ <strong> <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">ຈຸດຂາຍ (Point of "
"Sale)</font></strong> ຈັດການການຂາຍລົດຖີບ ແລະ ອຸປະກອນເສີມໂດຍກົງພາຍໃນຮ້ານ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"The<strong> <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">Sales App</font></"
"strong> create and manage quotations and sales orders."
msgstr ""
"ແອັບ <strong> <font style=\"color: rgb(113, 75, 103);\">ການຂາຍ (Sales)</"
"font></strong> ສ້າງ ແລະ ຈັດການໃບສະເໜີລາຄາ ແລະ ໃບສັ່ງຂາຍ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"This module offers all the essential tools a bike shop needs to run daily "
"operations in one place. It covers everything from selling bikes; both "
"online through an eCommerce website and in-store with a point of sale "
"system, to managing\n"
"            repairs, maintenance services, and inventory."
msgstr ""
"ໂມດູນນີ້ສະໜອງເຄື່ອງມືທີ່ຈຳເປັນທັງໝົດທີ່ຮ້ານລົດຖີບຕ້ອງການເພື່ອດຳເນີນງານປະຈຳວັນໃນບ່ອນດຽວ. "
"ມັນກວມເອົາທຸກຢ່າງຕັ້ງແຕ່ການຂາຍລົດຖີບ; ທັງແບບອອນລາຍຜ່ານເວັບໄຊ eCommerce ແລະ "
"ພາຍໃນຮ້ານດ້ວຍລະບົບຈຸດຂາຍ (PoS), ໄປຈົນເຖິງການຈັດການ\n"
"            ການສ້ອມແປງ, ການບໍລິການບຳລຸງຮັກສາ, ແລະ ສາງສິນຄ້າ."

