#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You can access every installed App in your Odoo database on your main "
"dashboard."
msgstr "ທ່ານສາມາດເຂົ້າເຖິງທຸກໆແອັບທີ່ຕິດຕັ້ງໄວ້ໃນຖານຂໍ້ມູນ Odoo ຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ທີ່ໜ້າຈໍຫຼັກ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You completed that demo use case! There are millions of other ways to adapt "
"your Odoo setup to fit your business needs."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານໄດ້ເຮັດສຳເລັດກໍລະນີຕົວຢ່າງນັ້ນແລ້ວ! ຍັງມີອີກຫຼາຍລ້ານວິທີທີ່ຈະປັບແຕ່ງ Odoo "
"ຂອງທ່ານໃຫ້ເໝາະສົມກັບຄວາມຕ້ອງການຂອງທຸລະກິດ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You didn't import demo data? You can still do it. Go to Apps &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade your Bike Shop package and check the related box."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານບໍ່ໄດ້ນຳເຂົ້າຂໍ້ມູນຕົວຢ່າງບໍ? ທ່ານຍັງສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້. ເຂົ້າໄປທີ່ ແອັບ (Apps) &gt; Industries "
"&gt; Upgrade your Bike Shop package ແລະ ໝາຍຫ້ອງທີ່ກ່ຽວຂ້ອງ."

#. module: bike_shop
#: model_terms:ir.ui.view,arch_db:bike_shop.welcome_article_body
msgid ""
"You should be able to execute the following flows to have an overview of "
"various flows you can quickly execute with this package using Odoo."
msgstr ""
"ທ່ານຄວນຈະສາມາດດຳເນີນການຕາມຂັ້ນຕອນຕໍ່ໄປນີ້ ເພື່ອໃຫ້ເຫັນພາບລວມຂອງຂັ້ນຕອນຕ່າງໆ "
"ທີ່ທ່ານສາມາດເຮັດໄດ້ຢ່າງວ່ອງໄວດ້ວຍແພັກເກັດນີ້ໂດຍໃຊ້ Odoo."

